</ul>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BWilliam_Lawrence_Bragg.7CBragg.2C_William_Lawrence.5D.5D.2C_D._C._Phillips_and_H._Lipson1992"><a href="/wiki/William_Lawrence_Bragg" title="William Lawrence Bragg">Bragg, William Lawrence</a>, D. C. Phillips and H. Lipson (1992). <i>The Development of X-ray Analysis</i>. New York: Dover. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0486673162" class="internal">ISBN 0-486-67316-2</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Development+of+X-ray+Analysis&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BWilliam+Lawrence+Bragg%7CBragg%2C+William+Lawrence%5D%5D%2C+D.+C.+Phillips+and+H.+Lipson&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BWilliam+Lawrence+Bragg%7CBragg%2C+William+Lawrence%5D%5D%2C+D.+C.+Phillips+and+H.+Lipson&amp;rft.date=1992&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Dover&amp;rft.isbn=0-486-67316-2&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:X-ray_crystallography"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BPaul_Peter_Ewald.7CEwald_PP.5D.5D.2C_editor.2C_and_numerous_crystallographers1962"><a href="/wiki/Paul_Peter_Ewald" title="Paul Peter Ewald">Ewald PP</a>, editor, and numerous crystallographers (1962). <i>Fifty Years of X-ray Diffraction</i>. Utrecht: published for the <a href="/wiki/International_Union_of_Crystallography" title="International Union of Crystallography">International Union of Crystallography</a> by A. Oosthoek's Uitgeversmaatschappij N.V..</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Fifty+Years+of+X-ray+Diffraction&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BPaul+Peter+Ewald%7CEwald+PP%5D%5D%2C+editor%2C+and+numerous+crystallographers&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BPaul+Peter+Ewald%7CEwald+PP%5D%5D%2C+editor%2C+and+numerous+crystallographers&amp;rft.date=1962&amp;rft.place=Utrecht&amp;rft.pub=published+for+the+%5B%5BInternational+Union+of+Crystallography%5D%5D+by+A.+Oosthoek%27s+Uitgeversmaatschappij+N.V.&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:X-ray_crystallography"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Paul_Peter_Ewald" title="Paul Peter Ewald">Ewald, P. P.</a>, editor <a href="http://www.iucr.org/iucr-top/publ/50YearsOfXrayDiffraction/" class="external text" title="http://www.iucr.org/iucr-top/publ/50YearsOfXrayDiffraction/" rel="nofollow"><i>50 Years of X-Ray Diffraction</i></a> (Reprinted in pdf format for the IUCr XVIII Congress, Glasgow, Scotland, Copyright © 1962, 1999 International Union of Crystallography).</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BJohannes_Martin_Bijvoet.7CBijvoet_JM.5D.5D.2C_Burgers_WG.2C_H.C3.A4gg_G.2C_eds.1969"><a href="/wiki/Johannes_Martin_Bijvoet" title="Johannes Martin Bijvoet">Bijvoet JM</a>, Burgers WG, Hägg G, eds. (1969). <i>Early Papers on Diffraction of X-rays by Crystals (Volume I)</i>. Utrecht: published for the <a href="/wiki/International_Union_of_Crystallography" title="International Union of Crystallography">International Union of Crystallography</a> by A. Oosthoek's Uitgeversmaatschappij N.V..</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Early+Papers+on+Diffraction+of+X-rays+by+Crystals+%28Volume+I%29&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BJohannes+Martin+Bijvoet%7CBijvoet+JM%5D%5D%2C+Burgers+WG%2C+H%C3%A4gg+G%2C+eds.&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BJohannes+Martin+Bijvoet%7CBijvoet+JM%5D%5D%2C+Burgers+WG%2C+H%C3%A4gg+G%2C+eds.&amp;rft.date=1969&amp;rft.place=Utrecht&amp;rft.pub=published+for+the+%5B%5BInternational+Union+of+Crystallography%5D%5D+by+A.+Oosthoek%27s+Uitgeversmaatschappij+N.V.&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:X-ray_crystallography"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BJohannes_Martin_Bijvoet.7CBijvoet_JM.5D.5D.2C_Burgers_WG.2C_H.C3.A4gg_G.2C_eds.1972"><a href="/wiki/Johannes_Martin_Bijvoet" title="Johannes Martin Bijvoet">Bijvoet JM</a>, Burgers WG, Hägg G, eds. (1972). <i>Early Papers on Diffraction of X-rays by Crystals (Volume II)</i>. Utrecht: published for the <a href="/wiki/International_Union_of_Crystallography" title="International Union of Crystallography">International Union of Crystallography</a> by A. Oosthoek's Uitgeversmaatschappij N.V..</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Early+Papers+on+Diffraction+of+X-rays+by+Crystals+%28Volume+II%29&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BJohannes+Martin+Bijvoet%7CBijvoet+JM%5D%5D%2C+Burgers+WG%2C+H%C3%A4gg+G%2C+eds.&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BJohannes+Martin+Bijvoet%7CBijvoet+JM%5D%5D%2C+Burgers+WG%2C+H%C3%A4gg+G%2C+eds.&amp;rft.date=1972&amp;rft.place=Utrecht&amp;rft.pub=published+for+the+%5B%5BInternational+Union+of+Crystallography%5D%5D+by+A.+Oosthoek%27s+Uitgeversmaatschappij+N.V.&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:X-ray_crystallography"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
